   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">This process applies to all Space plants that have FSC and PRS technology. Licensee plants should contact their Space Global Technical Assistance Account Manager. </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">FSC and PRS are High Risk Systems obsolescence ranked – Unsupportable systems. The reason is that most (if not all) spare parts are not available for those systems. Plants must rely on in-house inventories, and because of the age of this equipment, in-house spare parts should not be considered a reliable solution.</li>
